targets.rawSql: SELECT gender, COUNT(*)  FROM employees.employees GROUP BY gender
SELECT e.first_name, e.last_name, e.gender, s.salary FROM employees e LEFT JOIN salaries s ON e.emp_no = s.emp_no WHERE s.to_date > NOW() ORDER BY salary DESC LIMIT 20
